擬定一具體可行的執行計畫，包括執行策略、執行機關、執行方式與配
套措施等，俾能提供民眾一個安全、便利的步行空間。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "70bdc452a205", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "321", "s": "1512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "交通政策與行政", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-0489de64-moex-00018', 'locality-0489de64', 'locality-0489de64-moex-113-341b1486', 'sub-locality-0489de64-01', NULL, 'essay', '行政機關執行行政行為時有許多需要依循的行政原則，如依法行政原
